To build this package use 'make' for default options or 'make ARG=VALUE'.
To install this package use 'make install'.

The installation details are customizable with make variables (ARG)
- prefix             Location of the package
- bindir             Location of the binaries
- datadir            Location of timer.wav
- backupdir          Location for backups
- backupfmt          Directory name format for the backups
- timer_repeats      Number of times timer.sh repeats playing timer.wav

Default values:
- prefix=/usr/local
- bindir=${prefix}/bin
- datadir=${prefix}/share/benni
- backupdir=${prefix}/backup>
- backupfmt="%Y-%m-%d-%H-%M-%S"
- timer_repeats=20
